1047
01:25:47,945 --> 01:25:50,239
[ALIENS GROWLING]

1048
01:26:24,148 --> 01:26:25,316
[GROWLS]

1049
01:27:08,276 --> 01:27:09,736
[CLICKS]

1050
01:27:16,159 --> 01:27:17,744
