Not my blood.

1063
01:30:34,107 --> 01:30:36,067
Not my...

1064
01:30:36,484 --> 01:30:37,944
Not...

1065
01:30:39,070 --> 01:30:40,405
...my...

1066
01:30:42,657 --> 01:30:44,450
Not my blood.

1067
01:30:45,243 --> 01:30:46,619
Not my blood.

1068
01:30:46,828 --> 01:30:48,371
Not my blood.

1069
