Sneak attacks at night.

1088
01:31:26,284 --> 01:31:27,702
You stop it!

1089
01:31:29,662 --> 01:31:32,749
We're the resistance, Ray.
They can't occupy this country.

1090
01:31:32,957 --> 01:31:36,294
