1110
01:32:31,933 --> 01:32:36,813
<i>Waiting to sail
Your worries away</i>

1111
01:32:38,731 --> 01:32:41,734
<i>So close your eyes
On Hushabye Mountain</i>

1112
01:32:41,984 --> 01:32:44,987
[RAY AND OGILVY GRUNTING]

1113
01:32:46,906 --> 01:32:51,369
<i>Wave goodbye
To cares of the day</i>

1114
01:32:52,120 --> 01:32:57,250
<i>And watch your boat
From Hushabye Mountain</i>

1115
01:32:57,458 --> 01:33:03,381
<i>Sail far away
From Lullaby Bay</i>

1116
01:34:13,284 --> 01:34:14,911
[CLATTERING]

1117
01:34:29,550 --> 01:34:31,677
[RACHEL SCREAMING]

1118
01:34:55,952 --> 01:34:58,788
Rachel? Rachel?

1119
