Bring out the Javelin!

1199
01:44:33,988 --> 01:44:36,282
Clear! Get from behind! Clear!

1200
01:44:42,622 --> 01:44:44,582
[RACHEL SCREAMING]

1201
01:44:45,500 --> 01:44:47,794
