1213
01:45:52,442 --> 01:45:53,443
SOLDIER 1:
It's opening.

1214
01:45:53,651 --> 01:45:55,194
SOLDIER 2:
It's opening. Keep them back.

1215
01:46:34,525 --> 01:46:36,110
Clear!

1216
01:46:36,319 --> 01:46:39,155
SOLDIER: No, keep them back,
keep them back. Come on, stay back.

